Storage and Transshipment

Storage and transshipment services

Transshipment and storage of cargo is the most important element of schemes of re-import and re-export of goods.

  • We will develop an optimal scheme for the purchase and delivery of the goods abroad.
  • We will select a platform for storing and transshipment of goods in the ports of Turkey and the FEZ.
  • We will plan the stages of delivery and transportation, reducing the number of transshipment operations as much as it possible.
  • We will select an equipment and prepare transport.
  • We organize reception, storage and packing.
